  <div class="colContent">
  <!--DROP YOUR CONTENT HERE -->

      <p>In many  ways, shopping on-line has surpassed shopping in-store. One of the <em>big</em> ways is the ability to read customer reviews to help decide what to buy.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>
 
      <p>PowerReviews' <em>Mobile Reviews</em> goes a long way to  fill the gap for people shopping in stores &ndash; easy-to-use customer reviews on their  mobile devices.&nbsp; With a few keystrokes, shoppers can find the information they need to choose the right product for them. Our tag-based reviews empower your shoppers <em>and</em> associates with relevant and timely information that&rsquo;s easy to digest on mobile devices, using our at-a-glance  Review Snapshots. </p>

      <p>Mobile Reviews significantly reduces the time it takes for customers to make a decision to buy, giving them the information they need, when they need it &ndash;  right before they buy (or, conversely, walk out needing to &ldquo;think about it&rdquo;). We call it a &ldquo;just-in-time&rdquo; research tool that boosts consumer confidence and helps shoppers make a decision before leaving the store, removing a major barrier to  closing the sale.</p>
      <p>The result  &ndash; lower walk-out and higher in-store conversion &ndash; for the retailer <em>and </em>the manufacturer.</p>
      <p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Provide your customers with useful and relevant information at the point of decision</li>
        <li>Empower your customers to choose the right product</li>
        <li>Help your associates remove key purchase obstacles</li>
        <li>Provide better service and customer experience in the store</li>
        <li>Net-net, increase conversion and reduce walk-out in the store</li>
        <li>And, drive repeat purchase with a more engaging and interactive in-store experience</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Features</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Covers all major mobile platforms, including iPhone, Blackberry, Palm, Windows and Android</li>
        <li>Includes at-a-glance Review  Snapshot&trade;, individual Ratings &amp; Reviews, and easy-to-use Product Search</li>
        <li>Customer experience optimized for in-store shopping experience</li>
      </ul>

